item.dc:creator: @chassy13 Chassy13
item.description:
@chassy13 wrote:

There could be a matter of different things.

A.) The client you are using may not support the items or objects inside the server.

B.) You account is glitched as said above, possibly from an Item ID being too high or something else.

C.) Your loading methods are damaged or corrupt.
